    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚石油公司签署法令禁止向以色列出口煤炭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/colombia-s-petro-signs-decree-banning-coal-exports-to-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗签署法令，禁止向以色列出口煤炭，以向总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡的政府施压，结束加沙冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/colombia-s-petro-signs-decree-banning-coal-exports-to-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 16:02:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员需要美联储在杰克逊霍尔签署协议才能保持股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/traders-need-fed-go-sign-in-jackson-hole-to-keep-stocks-rallying</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街押注美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔将在怀俄明州杰克逊霍尔举行的央行年度会议上确认降息。但随着争论从“他们会降息还是不会降息？”转变为“降息幅度有多大？”，股票交易员可能会感到失望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/traders-need-fed-go-sign-in-jackson-hole-to-keep-stocks-rallying</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 16:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
